t a single complex command consisting of no more than two sentences. This binds the spirit to a task for no longer than a week unless successfully withstood. (As per Spirit 3 Spirit Summons with 1 reach to change the primary factor to potency, 2 reaches to issues a complex command, and the Exceptional Success used from 5 successes used to increase the Primary Factor [Potency] by 1)%0a---%0a> !!!!!First Attainment: Name%0a> :Prerequisite: Info%0a> *Info%0a> %0a> %0a> !!!!!Second Attainment: Name%0a> :Prerequisite: Info%0a> *Info%0a> %0a> !!!!!Third Attainment: Name%0a> :Prerequisite: Info%0a> *Info%0a> %0a> !!!!!Fourth Attainment: Name%0a> :Prerequisite: Info%0a> *Info%0a> %0a> :Optional Arcana: Name%0a> *Info%0a> %0a> !!!!!Fifth Attainment: Name%0a> :Prerequisite: Info%0a> *Info%0a
